        | method |
        | POST   |
        | PUT    |

    Scenario Outline: <method> with header
      Given header by RESTful api:
      """
      {
        "key1": "value1",
        "key2": ["value2", "value3"]
      }
      """
      When <method> "/index"
      Then got request:
      """
      : [{
        method: '<method>'
        path: '/index'
        headers: {
          key1: ['value1']
          key2: ['value2', 'value3']
        }
      }]
      """
      And "http://www.a.com" got a "<method>" request on "/index"
      Examples:
        | method |
        | GET    |
        | DELETE |

